Ashu Kasim Rabo (amụrụ n'abalị iri abụọ n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 1984) bụ onye Ethiopia na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge onye nke gbadoro anya na ọkara marathon na ihe omume marathon
Ihe kacha mma ya bụ nkeji 68:56 na awa 2:23:09, n'otu n'otu.
O meriri na Istanbul Marathon nke (afọ 2010) na Xiamen Marathon nke (afọ 2012)

Ashu nọchitere anya Ethiopia na mba ụwa ugboro atọ: na 2003 IAAF World Half Marathon Championships, na 2006 IAAF World Road Running Championships, nakwa na mita 10,000 na 2007 All-Africa Games (ebe ọ bụ nke anọ).
O zoro na 2003 IAAF World Half Marathon Championships na Vilamoura, Portugal ma mechie na ebe iri anọ na asaa
N'ịgba ọsọ na 2006 IAAF World Road Running Championships, ọ mechara nke iri na asaa ma nyere ndị otu Ethiopia nke Dire Tune na Teyba Erkesso aka inweta ihe nrite ọlaọcha
Ọ gara n'ihu nwee ihe ịga nke ọma n'okporo ụzọ n'afọ sochirinụ dịka ọ bụ onye nke anọ na mita 10,000 na 2007 All-Africa Games
O meriri na 15K Boilermaker Road Race na 2008.
Ashu mere marathon mbụ ya na afọ 2009 Paris Marathon ma dekọọ nke kacha mma nke 2:25:49 maka ọnọdụ nke anọ. N'ọnwa Ọktoba, ọ gara Istanbul Marathon dị ka onye nke abụọ n'azụ Bizunesh Urgesa
Ọ gbara ọsọ na 2010 Prague Marathon ma mechie n'ọnọdụ nke atọ na oge nke 2:29:54. Ọ laghachiri Istanbul n'afọ ahụ wee ruo n'elu ikpo okwu na ọsọ ndekọ nke 2:27:25.

Ọ bidoro oge 2011 ya site na onye nke abụọ na Houston Marathon, gafee akara mgbe onye Ethiopia ibe ya Mamitu Daska. Ọ lụrụ Daska ọzọ na Paris Marathon na ọnwa Eprel wee merie onye iro ya, mana ọ bụ naanị nke isii n'ozuzu. N'ọnwa Ọktoba, ọ nwara ịgbachitere aha ya na Istanbul Marathon, mana ọ bịara nke anọ mgbe ndị Etiopia ndị ọzọ nwetara ihe nrite na asọmupi ụmụ nwanyị.
Ashu meriri na 2012 Xiamen International Marathon na oge kachasị mma nke 2:23:09

Na ọnwa Juun, ọ bụ onye nke abụọ na Freihofer's Run for Women 5K na New York. Na asọmupi nke abụọ ya na China n'afọ ahụ, ọ bụ onye nke abụọ na Feyse Tadese na Shanghai Marathon, gafere akara na 2:24:09 awa.

Ọkara marathon kacha mma bịara na afọ 2013 RAK Half Marathon na Febụwarị na-esote, ebe ọ gbara ọsọ 68:56 nkeji iji mechie ọzọ n'azụ Feyse Tadese na nke iri. Ọ nọ n'ọkwa nke anọ na Rome City Marathon na Machị wee merie na Lanzhou Marathon na June. Njem ya kachasị mma bụ nke ikpeazụ ya n'afọ: ọ bịara nke atọ na Shanghai Marathon n'ime oge nke 2:26:34.
Ashu bụ onye nke abụọ na asọmupi 2014 Seoul International Marathon, na-agwụ n'azụ Helah Kiprop.
